title: Fahrenheit - The Movie (Edited by Rauli75)
description:
This is the movie of a game called Fahrenheit, or Indigo Prophecy if you are in North America, From Quantic Dreams.

The story goes... Lucas is just a regular guy who mysteriously murders another guy in a restaurant restroom for no reason. the thing is, Lucas did not want to commit a murder and he also doesn&#039;t know why he did it. From then on, Lucas is disturbed by visions of a little girl so he decides to go after an answer for what&#039;s happening. Still in the beginning of the story you are going to meet Carla and Tyler, two cops who were assigned to the mysterious murder case.
